# Project Overview

This is a Next.js project with Supabase integration for a form builder application with the following structure:

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts
- [app](mdc:app) - Next.js App Router structure with admin and public routes
- [components/form-builder](mdc:components/form-builder) - Form builder components
- [lib/supabase](mdc:lib/supabase) - Supabase integration utilities

## Key Features

1. Form Builder - Allows creation and management of custom forms
2. Admin Panel - Secured admin interface for form management
3. Supabase Backend - For authentication, database, and storage
4. Role-based Access Control - Using permissions and roles
